---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import iconWorld from "@/assets/svgs/icon_world.svg";
import iconLeaves from "@/assets/svgs/icon_leaves.svg";
import piramid from "@/assets/imgs/piramid.png";
import iconLine from "@/assets/svgs/icon_line.svg";
---

<div class="container">
  <div class="presentation">
    <section>
      <Image class="iconWorld" src={iconWorld} alt="Icon World" />
    </section>
    <br />
    <p>
      Escape to a world where nature embraces contemporary comfortâ€”nestled in
      the vibrant jungles of Tulum.
    </p>
    <br />
    <p>
      Picture waking up to the beautiful songs of tropical birds, surrounded by
      the lush jungle in vibrant colors. Every day is like a new adventure
      waiting to happen
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="information">
    <div class="informationText">
      <section class="iconLeaves">
        <Image class="iconLeaves" src={iconLeaves} alt="Icon Leaves" />
      </section>
      <br />
      <p>
        Cenote Gardens offers <b>56 residential lots</b> that bring a unique opportunity
        to be part of an extraordinary living experience.
      </p>
      <br />
      <p>
        It is the perfect place for those looking for <b
          >a lifestyle respectful of nature</b
        > and the biodiversity of the Mayan jungle.
      </p>
      <br />
      <p>
        Ideal to find <b>privacy</b> and coexistence with other people seeking wellness,
        spirituality, and expansion of consciousness.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <section class="piramid">
        <center>
          <Image class="piramid" src={piramid} alt="Piramid Image" />
        </center>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="question">
    <section>
      <Image class="iconLine" src={iconLine} alt="Icon Line" />
    </section>
    <br />
    <h1>WHAT MAKES CENOTE GARDENS AN ENTICING INVESTIMENT OPORTUNITY</h1>
    <br />
  </div>
  <div class="characteristics">
    <div>
      <section>
        <h2>VISION OF SUSTENTABLE LIVING</h2>
      </section>
    </div>
    <div>
      <section>
        <h2>ESSENTIAL SERVICES AND CONNECTIVITY</h2>
      </section>
    </div>
    <div>
      <section>
        <h2>PRIVATE CENOTE AN LUXURIOUS AMENITIES</h2>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .presentation,
  .question {
    color: #355442;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 9rem;
  }
  .iconWorld,
  .iconLeaves,
  .piramid,
  .iconLine {
    display: block;
    margin: auto;
    width: 10rem;
  }
  .information,
  .characteristics {
    color: #355442;
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    padding: 9rem;
  }
  .information > div {
    width: 50%;
  }
  .piramid {
    width: 25rem;
  }
  h1 {
    padding: 5rem;
    font-size: 3.5rem;
  }
  .iconLine {
    width: 15rem;
  }
  .characteristics > div {
    width: 33%;
  }
</style>
